  "original_title": "\u0d87\u0db8\u0dd9\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0d9a\u0dcf\u0db1\u0dd4 \u0d86\u0dbb\u0dca\u0dae\u0dd2\u0d9a\u0dba \u0d9c\u0dd0\u0db1 IMF \u0d85\u0db1\u0dad\u0dd4\u0dbb\u0dd4 \u0d85\u0d9f\u0dc0\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "IMF warns about US economy",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "As the International Monetary Fund lowered its 2022 economic growth forecast for the United States from 2.9% to 2.3% at the end of June, the IMF warned that avoiding recession in the country will be extremely challenging.",
        "The International Monetary Fund has issued this warning with recent data showing that consumer spending in the United States is weakening."
      ],
